---
import { PixelErhuCursor } from "@/components/interactive/PixelErhuCursor";
import { DraggableSticker } from "@/components/interactive/DraggableSticker";
import { FloatingBallDemo } from "@/components/interactive/FloatingBallDemo";
import { MascotIsland } from "@/components/interactive/MascotIsland";
import { Badge, Button, Card, Flex, Heading, Text } from "@radix-ui/themes";
---

<PixelErhuCursor client:load />
<MascotIsland client:idle />
<DraggableSticker client:visible />

<section class="section-frame px-4 py-20 lg:px-0 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mb-10 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.9fr)_minmax(20rem,0.85fr)] lg:items-end">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.28em] text-cc-peach uppercase">互动层</p>
      <h2 class="site-section-title mt-4">像素二胡光标、吉祥物和悬浮球演示一起营造轻巧又可爱的陪伴感。</h2>
      <p class="site-section-copy mt-5">参考流畅可爱的网站表达方式，但保持边界清楚：浏览器里展示的是交互语言和产品心智，不是假装能直接控制你本地桌面的一层壳。</p>
    </div>

    <Card className="site-soft-card rounded-[2rem] !p-6">
      <Flex direction="column" gap="3">
        <Badge color="cyan" variant="soft" radius="full">本轮重点</Badge>
        <Heading size="5">这一层专门解决“页面不够灵”和“交互不够可爱”的问题。</Heading>
        <Text size="3" color="gray">像素二胡光标不再用带迟滞的大圆形跟随，也不再用图片；点击反馈改成更短促的像素火花，不再遮挡正文。</Text>
        <Button asChild radius="full" size="3">
          <a href="#download">去看下载区</a>
        </Button>
      </Flex>
    </Card>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.1fr)_minmax(0,0.9fr)] lg:items-stretch">
    <FloatingBallDemo client:visible />

    <Card className="site-soft-card rounded-[2rem] !p-6">
      <Flex direction="column" gap="4">
        <Badge color="violet" variant="soft" radius="full">交互说明</Badge>
        <Heading size="6">官网交互只做有意义的活泼感，不做噱头。</Heading>
        <div class="grid gap-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/72">
          <p>像素二胡光标只在桌面指针设备开启，并在 reduced motion 下自动关闭。</p>
          <p>拖拽贴纸只保留本地网页位置状态，不伪造更多“系统能力”。</p>
          <p>悬浮球面板明确是概念演示，不会冒充真实 desktop RPC 行为。</p>
          <p>页面动效应该让产品更灵动，而不是让信息层级继续打架。</p>
        </div>
      </Flex>
    </Card>
  </div>
</section>
